.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, swimming, soccer
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, turquise, light-blue
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person who likes brown is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who likes turquise##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Sport          | swimming  | skiing  | soccer |
| Color   | turquise | brown | light-blue     |

