.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, subway, scooter
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, writing, drawing
1. the person driving the subway is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person driving the subway and the person driving the scooter##2
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Transport   | scooter   | train  | subway  |
| Hobby   | chess | writing | drawing |

