.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, poppy, amaryllis
3 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, rabbit
1. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the owner of the ferret is between the person who growsamaryllis and the owner of the guinea-pig##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Flower       | amaryllis | orchid | poppy  |
| Pet   | rabbit    | ferret        | guinea-pig |

