.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, security-guard, musician
House: futuristic, palace, ranch-style
1. the security-guard is on the left of the futuristic house##1
2. the ranch-style house is between the futuristic house and the palace house##2
3. the firefighter is on the left of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Job   | firefighter | security-guard   | musician   |
| House         | palace | ranch-style | futuristic |

