.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-14::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, august, december
There 3 different types of food: lime, peach, apricot
1. the person eating lime is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person eating peach##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Birthday   | october | december | august |
| Food     | peach    | lime    | apricot |

