.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-16::.
3 different pets are kept: lizard, bird, mouse
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, video-games, photography
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the mouse##2
2. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the bird is the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Pet   | bird | lizard   | mouse   |
| Hobby         | photography  | gardening | video-games |

