.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-17::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bongani, old-henry
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, aconite, poppy
1. the old-henry-smoker is between the person who growsaconite and the bongani-smoker##2
2. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |      3      |
| Cigar   | bongani       | old-henry | pall-mall |
| Flower         | iris | poppy | aconite      |

