.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, april, august
There 3 different types of food: lime, tomato, plum
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person eating tomato##2
3. the person eating lime is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Birthday      | august | april   | december |
| Food   | plum  | lime | tomato   |

 